Termasuk dirimu.

927
01:24:50,835 --> 01:24:53,212
Kau bisa mati bersama mereka...

928
01:24:54,630 --> 01:24:57,592
atau kau bisa mati demi mereka.

929
01:24:59,594 --> 01:25:02,763
Astaga, kedua pilihan itu
sangat menggiurkan.

930
01:25:20,489 --> 01:25:23,284
Seluruh dunia, Marty.

931
01:25:23,367 --> 01:25:25,536
Berada di tanganmu, Dana.

932
01:25:26,579 --> 01:25:28,247
Tak ada cara lain.

933
01:25:29,373 --> 01:25:31,125
Kau harus tegar.

934
01:25:32,376 --> 01:25:34,211
Ya, Dana.

935
01:25:35,755 --> 01:25:37,840
Kau merasa tegar?

936
01:25:39,467 --> 01:25:41,802
Maafkan aku.

937
01:25:45,264 --> 01:25:46,849
Aku juga.

938
01:26:29,475 --> 01:26:31,268
Marty...

939
01:26:35,981 --> 01:26:37,858
Marty!

940
01:27:31,412 --> 01:27:33,289
Hei.

941
01:27:36,000 --> 01:27:38,294
Kau tahu...

942
01:27:41,547 --> 01:27:44,341
Kurasa Curt tidak punya sepupu.

943
01:27:52,016 --> 01:27:53,809
Bagaimana keadaanmu?

944
01:27:56,937 --> 01:27:59,231
Aku akan mati.

945
01:28:02,735 --> 01:28:05,321
Maafkan aku.

946
01:28:06,238 --> 01:28:08,908
Maafkan aku karena hampir menembakmu.

947
01:28:09,658 --> 01:28:12,077
Mungkin seharusnya aku...

948
01:28:12,161 --> 01:28:14,413
Hei, tidak.

949
01:28:15,831 --> 01:28:17,458
Aku mengerti.

950
01:28:30,513 --> 01:28:35,601
Maaf karena kau diserang manusia serigala
dan membuat dunia kiamat.

951
01:28:36,685 --> 01:28:37,978
Tidak.

952
01:28:38,938 --> 01:28:41,232
Hei, kau benar.

953
01:28:42,316 --> 01:28:44,485
Umat manusia...

954
01:28:50,783 --> 01:28:54,453
Saatnya memberi orang lain kesempatan...

955
01:29:05,214 --> 01:29:08,968
Para dewa raksasa yang jahat.

956
01:29:13,764 --> 01:29:16,517
Kuharap aku bisa melihat mereka.

957
01:29:16,600 --> 01:29:18,602
Sama.

958
01:29:20,437 --> 01:29:24,024
Itu baru akhir pekan yang menyenangkan.

